** Section &quot;Ceratopetalum&quot;
** Section &quot;Cymatopetalum&quot;
** Section &quot;Thiopetalum&quot;
* Subgenus &quot;Sigmatopetalum&quot;
** Section &quot;Spathopetalum&quot;
